// Cross-TU regression: an inline body declared in another source file
// references a `#n` parameter as the count of `lsr * n`. Before the fix, the
// retargeted body kept its foreign byte offsets on `Expr::IdentSpanned`, so
// the diagnostic frankenspan landed at an unrelated location in this file.

func main @a8 {
    lda #$0f
    lsrx(a, #2) -> a
}
